OL,4,CNew guidance on supporting transgender
OL,5,Cpupils in schools
OL,6, New guidance on supporting transgender
OL,7, children in schools has been published
OL,8, by the Scottish government.
OL,10,FMinisters said the guidance was
OL,11,Fdesigned to help schools and education
OL,12,Fauthorities "make decisions
OL,13,Feffectively".
OL,15,FIt also recognises the importance of
OL,16,F"privacy and safe spaces" for girls and
OL,17,Fboys within schools.
OL,19,FThe Scottish government said the advice
OL,20,Fwas not prescriptive and did not
OL,21,Fpromote transitioning.
